casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Barkan.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Barkan (1991), 60 Ohio St. 3d 608.]

(No. 91-816 — Submitted May 14, 1991 — Decided May 22, 1991.)

The resignation of Yale A. Barkan as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
